Health (Fees) Amendment Regulations 2020

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, make the following regulations under the Health Act 1997 .

29 September 2020

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

S. COURTNEY

Minister for Health

1. Short title
    These regulations may be cited as the Health (Fees) Amendment Regulations 2020 .

2. Commencement
    These regulations take effect on 30 September 2020.

3. Principal Regulations
    In these regulations, the Health (Fees) Regulations 2017 are referred to as the Principal Regulations.

4.
    The amendments effected by this regulation have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Health (Fees) Regulations 2017 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 29 September 2020

These regulations are administered in the Department of Health.
